        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Demons debase all they touch. One of your ancestors fell victim to their corruption, and you are burdened by that sin.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> divine</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Intimidation, Religion</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Acid Splash]</em>, 1st: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Fear]</em>, 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Enlarge]</em>, 3rd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Slow]</em>, 4th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Divine Wrath]</em>, 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Abyssal Plague]</em>, 6th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Disintegrate]</em>, 7th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Divine Decree]</em>, 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Divine Aura]</em>, 9th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Implosion]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Glutton's Jaw]</em>, advanced: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Swamp of Sloth]</em>, greater: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Abyssal Wrath]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magic</strong> The corruption of sin weakens a target's defenses or makes you more imposing. Either a target takes a -1 status penalty to AC for 1 round, or you gain a +1 status bonus to Intimidation checks for 1 round.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Demonic Blood Magic (Self)], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Demonic Blood Magic (Target)]</p>"
        },
